    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;m allergic to shellfish &#8211; which takes a whole lot of the fun out of going home to MA.  No lobster rolls, no clam chowder, I get to watch everybody else feast.</></>The last time I ate shellfish on purpose was in Baltimore and it was a crab feast.  Sooo good &#8211; not worth dying for &#8211; but close.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-15923' data-commentid="15923" data-postid="1018" data-belowelement="comment-15923" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anonymous" aria-label='Reply to Anonymous'>Reply</a>    </div>
