      <p>The first time I ever met my boyfriend&#8217;s parents was last summer when they were flying from Oregon to New York. When they got off the plane at 11pm, his mom was carrying 5lbs. worth of Dungeness crabs. We got back to Brooklyn and such as you did, covered our table in newspaper, and proceeded to stay up until 3:30 in the morning eating crabs and drinking wine. It is one of my favorite memories of New York&#8230;bringing a little west coast to the east coast. Thanks for the wonderful post!</p>
