    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I think this may be my first comment here though I&#8217;ve been reading a long time 🙂  I can&#8217;t believe how similar our stories are (I also went to Cal for undergrad and am currently here at UW for grad school) and look forward to your book event tomorrow evening!  I love how you&#8217;re not afraid to post pictures of the aftermath of a crab eating fest, wee!</p>
