      <p>TLH, I&#8217;ve been buying my Polaroid 600 film from < HREF="http://www.bhphotovideo.com/c/product/149385-USA/Polaroid_625477_600_Instant_Color_Print.html" REL="nofollow">B&#038;H<>.  It&#8217;s expensive, but the price is pretty good, compared to other places online.  And as for Polaroid Spectra film, I&#8217;ve stopped buying it.  You can still find it online &#8211; do a Google search, or try eBay &#8211; but it&#8217;s gotten too expensive for me.  Good luck!</></>Ross, you made day.  Thank you.</p>
